%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor ADMIN as Admin

participant UI as Governance Setup UI
participant BFF as Governance BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant GOV as Governance Service
participant REF as Governance Reference Service
participant DB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

ADMIN->>UI: Add EA checklist items
UI->>BFF: Save EA checklist
BFF->>ORCH: Start EA checklist flow
ORCH->>GOV: Save checklist items
GOV->>DB: Insert/Update governance_qa_checklist
GOV-->>ORCH: Save success
ORCH-->>BFF: Success
BFF-->>UI: Show saved checklist

ADMIN->>UI: Configure EA ownership rule
UI->>BFF: Save EA ownership setting
BFF->>ORCH: Start EA rule flow
ORCH->>REF: Validate release manager reference
REF->>DB: Query role/release manager reference
DB-->>REF: Reference response
REF-->>ORCH: Validation success
ORCH->>GOV: Save EA ownership rule
GOV->>DB: Insert/Update governance_qa_rule
GOV-->>ORCH: Save success
ORCH-->>BFF: Success
BFF-->>UI: Show saved EA rule

ADMIN->>UI: Open Access Management and save rules
UI->>BFF: Save access rules
BFF->>ORCH: Start access save flow
ORCH->>REF: Get role master if needed
REF->>DB: Query role reference
DB-->>REF: Roles
REF-->>ORCH: Reference response
ORCH->>GOV: Save access rules
GOV->>DB: Insert/Update governance_access_rule
GOV-->>ORCH: Save success
ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish GovernanceAccessSaved Event
ORCH-->>BFF: Success
BFF-->>UI: Show saved access rules
